      "text": "0. Stock Investing",
      "description": "\n        <strong>Stock Investing</strong> is the practice of buying ownership in publicly traded companies with the goal of long-term capital appreciation, income, or both.\n    \n        <h4>💡 Why It Matters</h4>\n        Stock investing allows individuals and institutions to participate in economic growth, hedge against inflation, and build wealth over time.\n    \n        <h4>📚 Includes</h4>\n        - Active &amp; passive investment strategies<br>\n        - Trading psychology<br>\n        - Risk-return trade-offs\n    \n        <h4>🔍 Related Topics</h4>\n        - Fundamental and technical analysis<br>\n        - Portfolio management<br>\n        - Market behavior and economic cycles\n      <br><h4 style=\"font-weight: var(--ds-font-weight-strong); font-size: 16.002px; line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height); margin: calc(var(--ds-md-zoom)*16px)0 calc(var(--ds-md-zoom)*12px)0; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: DeepSeek-CJK-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Oxygen, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><strong>Example Workflow</strong></h4><ol start=\"1\" style=\"margin: calc(var(--ds-md-zoom)*12px)0; padding-left: calc(var(--ds-md-zoom)*24px); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: DeepSeek-CJK-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Oxygen, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16.002px;\"><li><p style=\"font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\"><strong>Stock</strong>: AAPL (Apple Inc.).</p></li><li style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\"><strong>Technical</strong>:</p><ul style=\"margin-top: 4px; padding-left: calc(var(--ds-md-zoom)*24px);\"><li><p style=\"font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\">50-day MA crosses above 200-day MA (Golden Cross → Bullish).</p></li><li style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"><p style=\"font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\">RSI at 65 (neutral momentum).</p></li></ul></li><li style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\"><strong>Fundamental</strong>:</p><ul style=\"margin-top: 4px; padding-left: calc(var(--ds-md-zoom)*24px);\"><li><p style=\"font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\">P/E = 28 (vs. industry 25 → slightly overvalued).</p></li><li style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"><p style=\"font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\">Revenue growth: +8% YoY.</p></li></ul></li><li style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\"><strong>Action</strong>:</p><ul style=\"margin-top: 4px; padding-left: calc(var(--ds-md-zoom)*24px);\"><li><p style=\"font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\">Buy partial position on breakout above $180 (resistance).</p></li><li style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"><p style=\"font-size: var(--ds-md-font-size); line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height);\">Set stop-loss at $170 (-5.5%).</p></li></ul></li></ol><hr style=\"height: 1px; margin: calc(var(--ds-md-zoom)*12px)0; background: rgb(var(--ds-rgb-label-3)); border: none; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: DeepSeek-CJK-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Oxygen, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16.002px;\"><p style=\"font-size: 16.002px; line-height: var(--ds-md-line-height); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: DeepSeek-CJK-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Oxygen, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><strong>Final Tip</strong>: Combine technical and fundamental signals for higher confidence. Always adapt strategies to market conditions (e.g., bear markets favor defensive stocks).</p>",
